    <notes><![CDATA[
* removed endpoints code in favor of a xml definition and generic methods;
* support new API additions (fixes bug #) and removed deprecated methods;
* support a "source" option (fixes bug #);
* better validation of parameters;
* improved/fixed tests and added the possibility to run tests locally (without
  calling the live service);
* cosmetic CS changes (removed licence in source code, added vim folds etc...);
    ]]></notes>
